{"tid":125122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死3隻]吉林煉油廠燒焊釀爆炸　3名工人身亡","createTime":"2017-02-18T08:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T08:04:37.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0029ac50b8d6e10c9844fe450d2a5782f65c474","tid":125122,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:03:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170217/bkncn-20170217143854895-0217_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170217%2Fbkncn-20170217143854895-0217_05011_001.html&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=34636fe5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170217/bkncn-20170217143854895-0217_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n吉林省松原市一家煉油廠今日上午8時許發生爆炸，導致3人死亡。根據官方通報，涉事松原石油化工股份有限公司的江南項目，一個加氫車間為酸性水汽提裝置源料水罐頂部安裝儀表，進行燒焊作業時罐體發生閃爆，導致現場3名工人身亡。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸人民共和國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f03666708c69050a51df9ce3348afa6e13d66dd","tid":125122,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}